{
  "stem": "964.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we was sitting the whole day and breaking up the bricks, make them-- make them smaller and level off the driveway.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And while we were working, we got kicked, hit over the head.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was summertime, I'm talking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There's a guy, wanted to have water.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He asked the-- the-- the German if he can have some water.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He said, yeah, take the pail and go get some water.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So he drank water from the pail.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "While he was drinking water from the pail, he said, drink.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You asked for water.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Drink.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He said, I have enough.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "No, drink.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He drowned him in the pail.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Going back to Kalisz, there was a-- a-- a director from Jewish Theater there, Levine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "His son lives here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I met him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "His father had to walk in in-- in-- into the river and drown himself.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And all the Jews had to stay around and watch it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What-- in my case, let me go back what I wanted to talk to you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In my case, they caught me in the street and I was cutting-- breaking up these bricks for-- for the-- for the driver to straighten out.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So one-- and this was in a company that they-- they were doing telephone connections from the front to-- to headquarters.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They used to come with trucks forth and back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one driver came along and asked this German, says, give me one guy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So-- no, two or three guys I think he asked for.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, I was between that-- that group.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we came over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He showed us how to dismantle a head of flat tire.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And those, the trucks, they had rings.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Not like here-- we have by pressure.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So the rings-- so he showed me how to do it.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
